<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.9">
<l>paṉṉiya pāram pārmakaṭ koḻiyap pārata māperum pōril</l>
<l>maṉṉarkaḷ maṭiya maṇineṭun tiṇṭēr maittuṉark kuyttamā māyaṉ</l>
<l>tuṉṉumā taviyuñ curapuṉaip poḻiluñ cūḻnteḻu ceṇpaka malarvāy</l>
<l>teṉṉaveṉ ṟaḷikaḷ muraṉṟicai pāṭun tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one of great wonders who drove a bejeweled chariot, tall and sturdy,</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of [his] cousin,</l>
<l>So the oppressive burden on lady earth would cease</l>
<l rend="indent">and so the kings in the great Bhārata War would die,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi where bees sing melodies, humming “teṉṉa,”</l>
<l>On tall champaka flowers encircled by clinging mādhavi vines</l>
<l rend="indent">and groves of wild laurel.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
